& [SLMAuthoritySourceRails] is the authority contract for the SLM project before implementation
  + [contract_uuid] is 5ce91f17-4b7d-4e9a-8d69-b9b3d45e3c15
  + [slice_id] is SLM-01
  + [source_document] is slm_project/source_documents/2026-06-20_slm_intake/Dictated_SLM_Source.sop
  + [source_manifest] is slm_project/source_documents/2026-06-20_slm_intake/Source_Document_Manifest.sop
  + [canonical_specification] is slm_project/specifications/SLM_Canonical_Specification.sop
  + [prior_exploded_specification] is slm_project/specifications/SLM_Exploded_Specification.sop
  + [work_decomposition_explosion] is slm_project/specifications/SLM_Explosion_Round_2_Work_Decomposition.sop
  + [work_slice_index] is slm_project/planning/project_manager/SLM_Work_Slice_Index.sop
  + [status] is accepted_for_sop_contract_work

  & [AuthorityOrder] is the local authority stack for this project
    + [first] is direct current user instruction
    + [second] is preserved source document
    + [third] is active ReasoningFramework SOP governance
    + [fourth] is canonical SLM specification draft
    + [fifth] is exploded specifications and work decomposition
    + [sixth] is project manager slice index and slice files
    + [seventh] is implementation artifacts after formation
    = must: treat source text as provenance and constraint pressure
    = must: treat canonical and exploded specs as derived interpretation, not source replacement
    = must: route conflicts back through source preservation and SJS reprocessing

  & [FalseStartQuarantine] is the status of premature implementation
    + [path] is slm_prototype
    + [classification] is owned_by_current_conversation_before_framework_activation
    + [status] is quarantined_reference_not_authority
    = must: not use slm_prototype as governing implementation authority
    = may: inspect or reuse concepts only after implementation formation maps them to accepted contracts
    - never: allow false-start code to silently decide architecture

  & [SOPFirstExecutionRule] is the current phase boundary
    + [current_phase] is specification_contract_formation
    + [not_current_phase] is executable Python implementation
    = must: finish and review SOP contracts before new implementation work
    = must: keep each work slice independently reviewable
    = must: update project manager slice state after each completed slice

  ! [Slice01Complete] is accepted
    @ [support] source document, manifest, canonical draft, explosion documents, staged plan, and work index exist as separate artifacts
    @ [support] false-start implementation is explicitly quarantined

